<div class="help-content-wrap"><h3 id="sports">Sports</h3>
<ol>
<li><p>How do I place a bet?</p>
<p>You can place different kinds of bets: singles, multiples and system (combined) bets.</p>
<p>Multiple bets may be placed by combining different sports: football, tennis, basketball, etc.</p>
</li>
<li><p>What is the minimum and maximum stake for a bet and for a ticket?</p>
<p>The minimum stake is KES 50 per bet and total stake for a ticket is no less than KES 50.</p>
<p>The maximum stake is KES 500,000 per bet and total stake for a ticket is no more than KES 500,000.</p>
</li>
<li><p>What is the maximum payout?</p>
<p>The maximum payout is KES 1,000,000 while there is no limit for Jackpot payout.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Where can I see my Sport bets?</p>
<p>Login into your account, click on &quot;Me&quot; in the bottom of Home page, go to &quot;SPORTS BET HISTORY&quot; highlighted in green, then you can see both settled and unsettled bets.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Where can I see my Virtual bets?</p>
<p>Go to Virtuals and click on &quot;<img src="../../../../assets/app-virtual.png" alt="">&quot; on the top-right corner of the page. You will find a list of all bets you have placed.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Can I cancel a bet?</p>
<p>No. A confirmed bet cannot be cancelled for any reason.</p>
</li>
<li><p>What is a “Void Bet”?</p>
<p>&quot;Void Bet&quot; means the bet is nil or invalid. This occurs when an event is postponed, or the event result is unverifiable etc. Once the match has been set as void (with odd 1.00) the rest of the winning ticket will then be paid out. If you are unsure why your bet has been made Void, please contact us.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Where can I find statistics for real sports?</p>
<p>For your assistance, SportyBet Kenya provides statistical information on events as reference during betting.</p>
<p>Just click on &quot;<img src="../../../../assets/stats.jpg" alt="">&quot; in every single event detail page to take an advantage of this service.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Where I can find the results of an event that has ended?</p>
<p>For your assistance, SportyBet Kenya provides information about the results of events. Just click on “Results” from the home page to take an advantage of this service.</p>
</li>
<li><p>What is Live Betting?</p>
<p>Live Betting is an exciting form of wagering that allows you to place bets on events that are ongoing. The odds are dynamic and change in accordance to the course of the actual event, offering double excitement as you get to monitor the event during play.</p>
</li>
<li><p>What is banker?</p>
<p>A banker is a selection which a customer believes is certain to win. If a banker is selected, it will be included in every combination and must win in order to provide a return on the bet.</p>
</li>
</ol>
